To install, please run these commands:
$ ./waf configure build [--with-gtk3] [--disable-nls] --prefix=/usr
$ sudo ./waf install

Build dependencies (for a Ubuntu system, please refer to your distribution naming scheme for equivalent):
- libappindicator-dev
- libgee-dev
- libnotify-dev
- libgtk2.0-dev or libgtk-3-dev (with gtk3)
- valac >= 0.10.0 (without gtk3) or >= 0.13.2 (with gtk3)

